            Fusce dapibus, tellus ac cursus commodo, tortor mauris condimentum
            nibh, ut fermentum massa justo sit amet risus.</p>
        <p>
            <a class="btn btn-default" href="#" role="button">View details
                &raquo;</a>
        </p>
    </div>
</div>

